@HalvorEndrerud @J_Kiese Good evening!
Our apologies for this unpleasant situation. We would like to assure that airBaltic is not discriminating any of its passengers.
To better understand all the circumstances, as what exactly has happened, we kindly ask to send us more details: https://t.co/N04NoZd2An

@ivyowowo Good morning! Our apologies for the inconveniences caused due to flight cancellation. 
If you would like to submit us a claim afterwards, please do so via this form: https://t.co/N04NoZd2An
Team will review all the circumstances and look into it.

@viktors_k Labdien!
Informējam, ka sistēma jau rāda šādu paziņojumu.
Tāpat atgādinām, ka atļauto dokumentu skaitu var ietekmēt arī pasažiera pilsonība, kā arī citi nosacījumi: https://t.co/GQDz8gktpo https://t.co/yvptLK3Zof

@LuBrooo @PlaniesNFT @heyougly @s0meone_u_know Khmm, we will jump in here for our friends from @PlaniesNFT! 😎
You can check out all the merch, including hoodies on our online shop:
https://t.co/MKXY9cOOv6

@BearOveHay Good morning and sorry to hear about such unpleasant situation at the airport. To investigate this, we kindly ask you to submit us a claim: https://t.co/N04NoZd2An
Our Customer Relations department will get back to you.
Our apologies for the inconveniences.

@jurgisvitols Labdien! Atvainojamies par neērtībām. Globālo piegāžu ķēžu problēmu dēļ airBaltic īstermiņā izīrējusi dažas papildu lidmašīnas, lai nodrošinātu plānoto lidojumu grafiku.
Sīkāk: https://t.co/sh7bCNNYc9

Papildu jautājumu gadījumā, aicinām sazināties ar mums privāti.
